<lb n="0382a12" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a1201">「嚩日囉<note place="inline"><note n="0382002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝一【明】</note><note n="0382002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二【大】，一【明】</note><app n="0382002"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">一</rdg></app>合</note>　吽<note place="inline">引</note>　鼎<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a13" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a1301">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　吽<note place="inline">引</note>　悉鼎<note place="inline">二合引</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382a1401">「次說外隅歌樂供養賢聖大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0382a15" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a1501">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　帝<note place="inline">引</note>　帝<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline"><note n="0382003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一〕－【元】＊</note><note n="0382003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一【大】＊，〔－〕【元】＊</note><app n="0382003"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a16" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a1601">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　詀吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a17" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a1701">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　馱<note place="inline">引</note>　凍<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a18" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a1801">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　屯<note place="inline">引</note>　馱<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382a1901">「次說護門供養賢聖大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0382a20" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a2001">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　<g ref="#CB00763"/><g ref="#CB00763"/><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a21" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a2101">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　吽<note place="inline">引</note>　吽<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0382003"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a22" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a2201">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　鑁鑁<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a23" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382a2301">「嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　惡惡<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382a2401">「復次，此金剛部祕密曼<note n="0382004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拏＝挐【元】</note><note n="0382004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拏【大】，挐【元】</note><app n="0382004"><lem wit="【大】">拏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">挐</rdg></app>羅中入等儀軌，即
<lb n="0382a25" ed="T"/>彼如是所有法用，皆如降三世大曼拏羅引
<lb n="0382a26" ed="T"/>入法儀。金剛阿闍梨如是入已，即以金剛祕
<lb n="0382a27" ed="T"/>密金剛部三昧印、對印、小印、智印，作彼現前
<pb n="0382b" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0882.0382b"/>
<lb n="0382b01" ed="T"/>執金剛供養事。所謂旋舞等諸作用，即彼如
<lb n="0382b02" ed="T"/>是旋舞、對舞、小舞、智舞，是為作用印智。謂先
<lb n="0382b03" ed="T"/>以彼金剛界攝受心明及金剛歌歌詠稱讚
<lb n="0382b04" ed="T"/>一切如來，作已然後金剛阿闍梨應當開示
<lb n="0382b05" ed="T"/>薩埵金剛印，後以應用入印所應入者現
<lb n="0382b06" ed="T"/>前引入：</p>
<lb n="0382b07" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0382b0701" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「當依金剛旋舞法，<caesura/>即以二手忿怒指，</l>
<lb n="0382b08" ed="T"/><l>依法當於自心間，<caesura/>結彼降三世大印。</l>
<lb n="0382b09" ed="T"/><l>然後旋舞如儀軌，<caesura/>以彼金剛忿怒鉤，</l>
<lb n="0382b10" ed="T"/><l>普遍鉤召諸如來，<caesura/>舉金剛箭善射相。</l>
<lb n="0382b11" ed="T"/><l>由金剛箭善射故，<caesura/>即得金剛喜成就，</l>
<lb n="0382b12" ed="T"/><l>次當解印如所說，<caesura/>齊掌結縛而摧拍。</l>
<lb n="0382b13" ed="T"/><l>如是供養大儀軌，<caesura/>當得金剛手歡喜，</l>
<lb n="0382b14" ed="T"/><l>由彼聖尊歡喜因，<caesura/>剎那所樂事成就。</l></lg>
<lb n="0382b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382b1501">「此等三昧印大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0382b16" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382b1601">「悉<g ref="#CB00833"/>嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382b17" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382b1701">「阿<note place="inline">引</note>　那野嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382b18" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382b1801">「囉<note place="inline">引</note>　誐野嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382b19" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382b1901">「娑<note place="inline">引</note>　度嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382b2001">「次當以彼對舞作用事供養：</p>
<lb n="0382b21" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0382b2101" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「亦如金剛旋舞相，<caesura/>左手當執右手拳，</l>
<lb n="0382b22" ed="T"/><l>旋轉還復額前安，<caesura/>頭指次應置於口，</l>
<lb n="0382b23" ed="T"/><l>旋舞又作日輪相，<caesura/>是印旋轉能普召，</l>
<lb n="0382b24" ed="T"/><l>次應竪立金剛幢，<caesura/>作喜笑相金剛笑。</l>
<lb n="0382b25" ed="T"/><l>如是供養大儀軌，<caesura/>能令國王等人眾，</l>
<lb n="0382b26" ed="T"/><l>咸生敬愛惠威光，<caesura/>或施財寶或歡喜。</l></lg>
<lb n="0382b27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382b2701">「此等對印大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0382b28" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382b2801">「阿<note place="inline">引</note>　呬嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<pb n="0382c" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0882.0382c"/>
<lb n="0382c01" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c0101">「入嚩<note place="inline">二合引</note>　羅野嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c02" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c0201">「禰<note place="inline">引</note>　呬嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c03" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c0301">「訶娑訶娑嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c04" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0382c0401" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「又復解其旋舞相，<caesura/>二拳齊密而相合，</l>
<lb n="0382c05" ed="T"/><l>頭指復安於心間，<caesura/>頂禮意生於戰悚，</l>
<lb n="0382c06" ed="T"/><l>次應又作旋舞相，<caesura/>能斷金剛利劍尊，</l>
<lb n="0382c07" ed="T"/><l>旋轉其相復如輪，<caesura/>是為旋轉輪壇相。</l>
<lb n="0382c08" ed="T"/><l>以金剛語妙歌詠，<caesura/>供養金剛手聖尊，</l>
<lb n="0382c09" ed="T"/><l>如是供養大法儀，<caesura/>一切究竟得成就。</l></lg>
<lb n="0382c10" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382c1001">「此等小印大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0382c11" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c1101">「哥<note place="inline">引</note>　野嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c12" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c1201">「親那野嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c13" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c1301">「勃囉<note place="inline">二合引</note>　摩野嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c14" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c1401">「沒嚕<note place="inline">二合引</note>　呬嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c15" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0382c1501" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「次竪金剛忿怒指，<caesura/>即復仰起面相合，</l>
<lb n="0382c16" ed="T"/><l>後復旋轉置頂間，<caesura/>頭指還於口門住，</l>
<lb n="0382c17" ed="T"/><l>金剛羯磨依法用，<caesura/>作諸事業勝壇場，</l>
<lb n="0382c18" ed="T"/><l>顯示隨應旋舞儀，<caesura/>後復於自心安置。</l>
<lb n="0382c19" ed="T"/><l>依法次應作旋舞，<caesura/>結縛是為金剛護，</l>
<lb n="0382c20" ed="T"/><l>相合二手金剛牙，<caesura/>二金剛拳相逼附。</l>
<lb n="0382c21" ed="T"/><l>如是供養大法儀，<caesura/>能成一切羯磨法，</l>
<lb n="0382c22" ed="T"/><l>如是四種供養儀，<caesura/>解印如應依本教。</l></lg>
<lb n="0382c23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382c2301">「此等智印大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0382c24" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c2401">「涅哩<note place="inline">二合</note>　爹嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c25" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c2501">「犖叉嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c26" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c2601">「珂<note place="inline">引</note>　那嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c27" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0382c2701">「滿馱嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0382c28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0382c2801">「復次，教授忿怒金剛印智：</p>
<pb n="0383a" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0882.0383a"/>
<lb n="0383a01" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0383a0101" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「二手執彼金剛杵，<caesura/>起忿怒意作破壞，</l>
<lb n="0383a02" ed="T"/><l>隨欲破者某甲名，<caesura/>以所執杵破其心，</l>
<lb n="0383a03" ed="T"/><l>下脣附齒而相合，<caesura/>隨欲破者應摧逼，</l>
<lb n="0383a04" ed="T"/><l>若有違越教勅者，<caesura/>速當破壞其頭頂。</l>
<lb n="0383a05" ed="T"/><l>金剛忿怒大觀視，<caesura/>二目隨應瞬動間，</l>
<lb n="0383a06" ed="T"/><l>所欲破者即當觀，<caesura/>彼即二目俱破壞。</l>
<lb n="0383a07" ed="T"/><l>金剛忿怒相合故，<caesura/>於自心中觀自身，</l>
<lb n="0383a08" ed="T"/><l>以金剛縛逼附間，<caesura/>即彼惡者心破壞。</l></lg>
<lb n="0383a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0383a0901">「此等大明曰：</p>
<lb n="0383a10" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383a1001">「吽<note place="inline">引</note>　嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　塞怖<note place="inline">二合引</note>　吒姹<note place="inline">入<note n="0383001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲＋（一句）【明】</note><note n="0383001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聲【大】，聲一句【明】</note><app n="0383001"><lem wit="【大】">聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">聲一句</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0383a11" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383a1101">「吽<note place="inline">引</note>　目珂嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　姹<note place="inline"><note n="0383002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">入＋（聲一句）【明】＊</note><note n="0383002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">入【大】＊，入聲一句【明】＊</note><app n="0383002"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲一句</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0383a12" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383a1201">「吽<note place="inline">引</note>　嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　泥<note place="inline">引</note>　怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　<note n="0383003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姹＋（入聲一句）細註【明】</note><note n="0383003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">姹【大】，姹<note place="inline">入聲一句</note>【明】</note><app n="0383003"><lem wit="【大】">姹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">姹<note place="inline">入聲一句</note></rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0383a13" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383a1301">「吽<note place="inline">引</note>　摩弩<note place="inline">引</note>　嚩日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　姹<note place="inline"><app type="star" corresp="#0383002"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">入聲一句</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0383a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0383a1401">「復次，教授大金剛部祕密印智，此中最先應
<lb n="0383a15" ed="T"/>結大印：</p>
<lb n="0383a16" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0383a1601" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「安布金剛忿怒拳，<caesura/>二手小指相鉤結，</l>
<lb n="0383a17" ed="T"/><l>左手三叉相背安，<caesura/>此名降三世大印。</l>
<lb n="0383a18" ed="T"/><l>左手頭指次展舒，<caesura/>即以此指當上起，</l>
<lb n="0383a19" ed="T"/><l>後應旋轉亦復然，<caesura/>還於左面金剛住。</l>
<lb n="0383a20" ed="T"/><l>齊掌應作金剛縛，<caesura/>起忿怒意而隱覆，</l>
<lb n="0383a21" ed="T"/><l>堅竪大指如金剛，<caesura/>忿怒帝哩帝哩印。</l>
<lb n="0383a22" ed="T"/><l>作拳先屈二頭指，<caesura/>即復二指如鉤相，</l>
<lb n="0383a23" ed="T"/><l>二頭指面如金剛，<caesura/>後二頭指彈指相，</l>
<lb n="0383a24" ed="T"/><l>二頭指面如金剛，<caesura/>心中復示日輪相，</l>
<lb n="0383a25" ed="T"/><l>竪二頭指頂間安，<caesura/>旋轉還至於笑處，</l>
<lb n="0383a26" ed="T"/><l>竪二頭指緊密相，<caesura/>二拳猶如執劍勢，</l>
<lb n="0383a27" ed="T"/><l>相合二頭指如輪，<caesura/>竪二大指向口散，</l>
<lb n="0383a28" ed="T"/><l>次復應舒二頭指，<caesura/>後二頭指纏其<note n="0383004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唳＝喉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0383004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唳【大】，喉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0383004"><lem wit="【大】">唳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】 【元】 【明】 【宮】">喉</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0383a29" ed="T"/><l>二手如牙口邊住，<caesura/>堅密二手成拳相。</l></lg>
<pb n="0383b" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0882.0383b"/>
<lb n="0383b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0383b0101">「如是分別大印次第。</p>
<lb n="0383b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0383b0201">「次結金剛部祕密三昧印：</p>
<lb n="0383b03" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0383b0301" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「從祕密拳所出生，<caesura/>此說是即諸三昧，</l>
<lb n="0383b04" ed="T"/><l>我今說彼成結儀，<caesura/>而金剛結勝無上。</l>
<lb n="0383b05" ed="T"/><l>先以二拳安於心，<caesura/>次復二拳置兩脇，</l>
<lb n="0383b06" ed="T"/><l>鉤召持箭悉左邊，<caesura/>後復從心而起散。</l>
<lb n="0383b07" ed="T"/><l>次顰眉尊寶旋轉，<caesura/>後當作彼日輪相，</l>
<lb n="0383b08" ed="T"/><l>舒臂亦應頂上安，<caesura/>旋轉還置於笑處。</l>
<lb n="0383b09" ed="T"/><l>二拳向口善安置，<caesura/>次持利劍揮斫相，</l>
<lb n="0383b10" ed="T"/><l>下擲其輪表示相，<caesura/>後復二拳向口散。</l>
<lb n="0383b11" ed="T"/><l>身曼拏羅頂最勝，<caesura/>二肩次心復二脇，</l>
<lb n="0383b12" ed="T"/><l>作金剛護亦復然，<caesura/>牙相堅固拳逼附。</l>
<lb n="0383b13" ed="T"/><l>外曼拏羅諸印契，<caesura/>結中<note n="0383005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">標＝幖【元】</note><note n="0383005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">標【大】，幖【元】</note><app n="0383005"><lem wit="【大】">標</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">幖</rdg></app>幟如次第，</l>
<lb n="0383b14" ed="T"/><l>是即三昧金剛縛，<caesura/>及金剛拳亦如是。</l></lg>
<lb n="0383b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0383b1501">「復次，宣說金剛部法印，所<note n="0383006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謂＝請【宮】</note><note n="0383006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謂【大】，請【宮】</note><app n="0383006"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">請</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb n="0383b16" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b1601">「發吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b17" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b1701">「設吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b18" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b1801">「摩吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b19" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b1901">「薩吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b20" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2001">「囉吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b21" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2101">「怛吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b22" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2201">「提哩<note place="inline">二合</note>　吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b23" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2301">「喝吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b24" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2401">「鉢吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b25" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2501">「怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>　吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b26" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2601">「葛吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b27" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2701">「嚩吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383b28" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383b2801">「酤吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<pb n="0383c" ed="T" xml:id="T18.0882.0383c"/>
<lb n="0383c01" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383c0101">「哩吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383c02" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383c0201">「朅吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383c03" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT18p0383c0301">「未吒<note place="inline">一句</note></p>
<lb n="0383c04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT18p0383c0401">「次結金剛部祕密羯磨印：</p>
<lb n="0383c05" ed="T"/><lg type="regular" xml:id="lgT18p0383c0501" style="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「所有羯磨印次第，<caesura/>謂金剛拳依法作，</l>
<lb n="0383c06" ed="T"/><l>依教隨處如應安，<caesura/>忿怒視即忿怒法。」</l></lg></cb:div>
<lb n="0383c07" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="012" fun="close"><cb:jhead>佛說一切如來真實攝大乘現證三昧大教王
<lb n="0383c08" ed="T"/>經卷第十二</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
</body></text></TEI>